E.I3: Carbon offsets are a massive scam.
"Carbon credits" are nothing more than a free ticket to pollute in return for a promise that a piece of forest is preserved.

PRESERVED, not restored. In most cases, all the money that does not go towards middlemen, go towards preventing an already protected forest from being cut down based on massively overblown population and/or economic growth estimates.

In essence: "Can we pollute? We will give some money to this person who will use that money to overestimate the potential damage to a distant tiny chunk of rainforest that is already protected. The small amount of leftover money can then go to the corrupt government of that small third world country." Nothing is done, no changes are made, some rich people get richer.
